{"tid":1929913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴菲特的股票持倉近一個月蒸發800億美元","createTime":"2020-03-17T08:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T09:12:23.000Z","uid":54867,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5bc001877019f835c7a54152decc23b893ca6a","tid":1929913,"uid":54867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:31:29.000Z","msg":"根據知名美股網站GuruFocus的計算，自2月19日美股開始墮入熊市以來，「股神」巴菲特的股票投資組合已經損失約802億美元，跌幅為32%。<br />\n<br />\n其中，巴菲特的前三大持倉蘋果、美國銀行和可口可樂分別虧損199.5億美元、132億美元和58億美元。今年迄今，巴菲特投資組合的市值下跌713億美元，跌幅為29%。同期，標普500指數下跌了26%。<br />\n<br />\n據伯克希爾2月15日公佈的最新13F表格顯示，伯克希爾四季度前五大重倉股依次為：蘋果、美國銀行、可口可樂、美國運通、富國銀行，佔總持倉比例依次為29.74%、13.46%、9.14%、7.8%、7.12%，前五大重倉股合計佔總持倉比約為67%。<br />\n<br />\n又要輸比大家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce32436189400f1f74e8861b72e1734d0a91f6c7","tid":1929913,"uid":54867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:32:52.000Z","msg":"補返個source: 富途牛牛<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.futunn.com/market/116381?src=1&amp;user_id=696901&amp;auth_token=815986&amp;clienttype=12&amp;clientver=10.1.736&amp;clientlang=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.futunn.com%2Fmarket%2F116381%3Fsrc%3D1%26user_id%3D696901%26auth_token%3D815986%26clienttype%3D12%26clientver%3D10.1.736%26clientlang%3D1&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8BZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b5c43c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.futunn.com/market/116381?src=1&amp;user_id=696901&amp;auth_token=815986&amp;clienttype=12&amp;clientver=10.1.736&amp;clientlang=1</a>"},{"pid":"9a7483f2c295fb7b8767fbca616b8384d06e5b69","tid":1929913,"uid":111153,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"正股驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf30b9cab5d454af8e9e2b8361d922fe6588c92","tid":1929913,"uid":16